Changes to this Privacy Policy
Pedi STAT Software reserves the right to revise or update this Privacy Policy at any time. In the event that significant changes are made, Pedi STAT Software commits to advising all users at the time that any significant change is made. If we make material changes to this policy, we will notify you here, by email, or by means of a notice on our home page or app.
If we decide to change our privacy policy, we will post those changes to this Privacy Policy and other places we deem appropriate so that you are aware of what information we collect, how we use it, and under what circumstances, if any, we disclose it.
